name: v21-native-nested-tuple-pattern
---

# Nested tuple pattern

```scalascript
def first(pair: Any): String =
  val pick = value =>
    val (left, ignored) = value
    left
  pick(pair)

def render(value: Any): String = value match {
    case Some((left, '+', right)) => left ++ "+" ++ right
    case None => "none"
  }

println(first(("left", "ignored")))
println(render(Some(("left", '+', "right"))))
```
